%S A395867 1,1,1,4,6,19,49,143,403,1238,3703,11490,35621,112164
%N A395867 Number of oriented polyominoes in the {3,7} tessellation of the hyperbolic plane.
%C A395867 For oriented polyominoes, chiral pairs are counted as two.
%H A395867 <a href="https://oeis.org/wiki/PF-Non-Euclidean">Wiki page indexing sequences related to non-euclidean polyforms</a>
%F A395867 a(n) = P{p,q}(n) (the number of oriented {p,q} polyominoes of size n) is equal to P{p,oo}(n) for n <= q. In this case, P{p,oo}(n) = A001683(n+2).
%t A395867 (* Cf. A394862 with p=3 and q=7. *)
%Y A395867 Cf. A001683, A330659, A394862.
%K A395867 nonn,more,new
%O A395867 1,4
